\subsection*{Load-In \& Parking}
Because we travel with heavy equipment and road cases, we require the shortest possible, barrier-free access route (ramp or elevator) from the loading dock directly to the stage.

<% if total_vans > 0 %>
We will arrive with a total of \textbf{<< total_vans >> vehicles} 
<% if config.anreise is defined and config.anreise.fahrzeuge is defined %>
    (<% if mat_vans > 0 %><< mat_vans >> Box Trucks / Cargo Vans<% endif %><% if mat_vans > 0 and pers_vans > 0 %> and <% endif %><% if pers_vans > 0 %><< pers_vans >> Passenger Vehicles<% endif %>).
<% endif %>
<% endif %>

